How to install and use the Pizza.py (or LPP) software package:

Github repository: https://github.com/CFDEMproject/LPP

Installation and running instruction: https://www.cfdem.com/forums/liggghts-installation-guide-ubuntu-1204-lts-and-1304

Install:
$ sudo apt-get install python-numpy
$ sudo git clone https://github.com/CFDEMproject/LPP.git $HOME/LPP
$ gedit ~/.bashrc
add at the bottom: alias lpp="python $HOME/LPP/src/lpp.py"

Run:
$ cd ~/Plasticity_Project/post
$ lpp dump*.Shear

